# =========================================================

# Server Standards

# 微信小游戏 Go 服务端开发规范

# =========================================================

## Tech Stack

# 使用 Go 1.26

* Use Go 1.26

# Gin 用于必要 HTTP 接口

* Use Gin only for required HTTP APIs

# HTTP JSON REST 为核心协议

* Use HTTP JSON REST under `/api/v1` as the primary client/server protocol

# Gin 处理 HTTP 路由

* Use Gin for HTTP routing and middleware; keep handlers thin

# 使用 ent ORM

* Use ent ORM

# 使用 PostgreSQL

* Use PostgreSQL

# 使用 Redis

* Use Redis

## Project Goals

# 服务端目标：轻度放置 RPG

* The backend serves a mobile idle RPG game

# 优先稳定和快速迭代

* Prioritize stability and fast iteration

# 架构保持简单易维护

* Keep architecture simple and maintainable

# 避免过早分布式设计

* Avoid premature distributed architecture

# 优先 AI Native 工作流

* Prefer AI-assisted iterative development workflows

## Architecture

# 使用模块化单体架构

* Use modular monolith architecture

# 业务逻辑放 service 层

* Keep gameplay logic inside service layer

# handler/gateway 保持轻量

* Keep handlers and gateways thin

# 网关、玩法、持久化分层

* Separate gateway, gameplay, and persistence logic

# 使用模块化目录结构

* Prefer modular package structure

# 避免循环依赖

* Avoid circular dependencies

# 优先复用已有模式

* Reuse existing patterns before introducing abstractions

# 避免过度接口化

* Avoid unnecessary interfaces and abstractions

# 禁止微服务化

* Do not introduce microservices during MVP

## Gameplay

# 游戏逻辑尽量以内存计算

* Gameplay systems should primarily run in memory

# 避免频繁写数据库

* Avoid excessive database writes during gameplay

# 优先批量落库

* Prefer batch persistence when possible

# Redis 用于缓存/排行/在线状态

* Redis should be used for cache, ranking, and online state

# PostgreSQL 用于永久数据

* PostgreSQL should be used for persistent player data

# 配置驱动数值系统

* Prefer configuration-driven gameplay balancing

## Database

# 使用 PostgreSQL 特性

* Leverage PostgreSQL strengths appropriately

# JSONB 可用于扩展玩法数据

* JSONB may be used for extensible gameplay metadata when appropriate

# 避免 N+1 查询

* Avoid N+1 queries

# 大数据使用分页

* Use pagination for large datasets

# 优先批量操作

* Prefer batch operations

# 禁止危险全表更新

* Avoid dangerous full table updates/deletes

# 禁止 destructive migration

* Never generate destructive schema migrations automatically

# 使用渐进式 schema 演化

* Prefer incremental schema evolution

# schema 必须保持清晰稳定

* Keep schema evolution explicit and maintainable

## Redis

# redis key 集中管理

* Centralize redis keys as constants

# 使用清晰 key 命名

* Use clear redis key naming conventions

# 避免重复缓存逻辑

* Avoid duplicated cache logic

## Networking

# 协议文档在 docs 仓库

* API contract lives in `docs/api/http-v1.md`; update docs when changing endpoints

# HTTP JSON 为主协议

* Use `/api/v1` JSON REST for gameplay; Bearer tokens for authenticated routes

# 类型定义在 apitypes

* Define request/response structs in `internal/apitypes` with explicit JSON tags

# 会话 token 替换

* New login invalidates prior session tokens for the same player

# handler 保持薄

* Parse JSON, validate session, call services; no business logic in handlers

# 避免高频轮询

* Avoid unnecessary high-frequency polling; batch client actions when possible

## HTTP API

# 保持向后兼容

* Prefer additive JSON fields; never reuse field meanings without version bump

# 禁止 giant payload

* Avoid giant universal JSON blobs in responses

# 保持消息显式清晰

* Keep API types explicit in `internal/apitypes`

# 避免过度嵌套结构

* Avoid deeply nested JSON without need

## Code Style

# 函数保持小而清晰

* Keep functions small and readable

# 显式逻辑优先

* Prefer explicit logic over magic abstractions

# 正确使用 context.Context

* Use context.Context correctly

# 显式错误处理

* Handle errors explicitly

# 避免滥用 goroutine

* Avoid unnecessary goroutines

# 避免过度设计

* Avoid over-engineering

# 优先可读性

* Prioritize readability over cleverness

## Testing

# 核心玩法增加单测

* Add unit tests for important gameplay logic when appropriate

# 完成任务前确保可编译

* Ensure code compiles before task completion

# 未要求时避免 fake/mock

* Avoid fake/mock implementations unless requested

## AI Collaboration

# 优先渐进式开发

* Prefer incremental implementation steps

# 一次只实现一个明确模块

* Implement one focused module at a time

# 避免一次生成整个系统

* Avoid generating entire large systems at once

# 优先稳定模式

* Prefer stable and repeatable patterns

# 保持代码 AI 可维护

* Keep code easy for future AI agents to understand

## Restrictions

# 禁止修改客户端目录

* Do not modify client directory

# 未批准禁止修改项目结构

* Do not change project structure without approval

# 禁止引入无必要依赖

* Do not introduce unnecessary dependencies

# 禁止重写无关系统

* Do not rewrite unrelated systems

# 禁止提前复杂化基础设施

* Avoid premature infrastructure complexity

# 禁止引入 Kubernetes / Service Mesh

* Do not introduce Kubernetes or service mesh during MVP

# 禁止企业级架构模式

* Avoid enterprise-scale architecture patterns during MVP
